---
layout: layouts/base.njk
eleventyNavigation:
  key: Supporters
  order: 4
---


<div class="content">
  <div class="block">
    <div class="box">

          <p class="title">Patron List</p>
          <p class="subtitle">Futureporn.net continues to improve thanks to <strong>{{ patreon.patronCount }} generous supporters.</strong></p>

          {% set donorsAndPatrons = patreon.patrons.concat(donors.list) %}

          <div class="patron-list columns is-mobile is-multiline">
          {%- for patron in donorsAndPatrons %}

            <div class="column is-full-mobile is-half-tablet is-one-third-desktop">
              <div class="box">
                <article class="media">

                  <div class="media-content">
                    <div class="content">
                      {% if patron.username %}
                        <p>
                          <strong>{{ patron.username }}</strong>
                        </p>
                      {% endif %}
                      {% if patron.vanityLink %}
                      <a target="_blank" href="{{ patron.vanityLink }}">
                        <span>{{ patron.vanityLink }}</span>
                        <span class="icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span>
                      </a>
                      {% endif %}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            </div>
          {% endfor %}
          </div>

          <p>Want to get your name on this list, and get perks like FAST video streaming on select VODs? <a href="https://patreon.com/CJ_Clippy" target="_blank">Become a patron today!<span class="icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></a><p>Patron names are private by default-- <a href="/profile">Opt-in</a> to have your name displayed.</p>


        </div>

  </div>
</div>